articles.title: 'You are not my king,' Indigenous Australian senator yells at visiting King Charles - ABC News
articles.description: An Indigenous senator told King Charles III that Australia is not his land as the British royal visited Australia’s parliament
articles.content:
CANBERRA, Australia -- An Indigenous senator told King Charles III that Australia is not his land as the British royal visited Australias parliament on Monday.
